WEBVTT

00:03:26.458 --> 00:03:30.851
Ammo ming afsuski, ko'plab afrikalik
talantlar to'g'ri chetga ketishyapti,

00:03:30.875 --> 00:03:32.643
boshqa mamlakatlarga.

00:03:32.667 --> 00:03:33.934
Masalan,

00:03:33.958 --> 00:03:37.268
bu nigeriyalik shifokor 
tug'ilmagan chaqaloqni operatsiya qilgan

00:03:37.292 --> 00:03:38.559
Texasda.

00:03:38.583 --> 00:03:40.226
Bu nigeriyalik shifokor ham

00:03:40.250 --> 00:03:44.809
atletlardagi chayqalishning
nevrologik ta'sirlarini kashf etgan.

00:03:44.833 --> 00:03:47.559
Ko'p mamlakatlarda afrikalik
atlerlar bor

00:03:47.583 --> 00:03:50.601
ular uchun oltin medal yutib beradigan.

00:03:50.625 --> 00:03:52.059
Qizig'i shundaki,

00:03:52.083 --> 00:03:54.559
biz Xudo Afrikani to'g'rilashini 
kutib o'tiribmiz.

00:03:54.583 --> 00:03:57.536
Rostdan, xazilsiz
biz kutib o'tiribmiz.

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:59.768
Ya'ni, shunchaki
Burundi prezidentiga qarang.

00:03:59.792 --> 00:04:02.184
U muxbirlar va muxolifat a'zolarini
qamamoqda,